longDesc:
Engine deposits are the silent killers of engines. They cause breakdowns that lead to unplanned
downtime and impact business. Engine deposits are a result of using poor functioning lubricants and
diesel fuel. This problem is made worse by the demanding driving conditions experienced by a
commercial vehicle.

PETRONAS Urania diesel engine oil range is formulated with ViscGuard™ technology to effectively guard
against engine deposits build-up, preventing abrasive wear and oxidation to maintain optimal oil
viscosity. It safeguards a commercial vehicle's most valuable asset - the engine, and keeps them going
for longer, ensuring commitments are met in full, day after day.

- Recommended to use in diesel driven commercial vehicles & generators.
name: Petronas Urania 800 20w-50 (API CF-4) 5 ltr

longDesc:
Bikes operate under high stress. Even under normal riding conditions, bikes experience high shear and
high temperature within a short period of time. This may translate to engine making rattling noises or
the bike may feel heavy or sluggish. The effects of bike stress will impact performance, fuel efficiency
and engine life.
PETRONAS Sprinta with UltraFlex™ technology is engineered with a unique formulation that enhances
oil stability to withstand the damaging effects of bike stress to keep your bike running quietly and
smoothly and at its best. PETRONAS Sprinta with UltraFlex™ technology resists bike stress and gives your
bike a longer life.
name: Petronas Sprinta F300 20w-50 (API SL) 1 ltr

longDesc:
Choosing the right Lubricant is very important to reduce excessive engine heat to prevent engine
damage.
PETRONAS SYNTIUM passenger car motor oil range is uniquely formulated with O CoolTech TM to defend
against excessive heat to maintain optimum engine performance. PETRONAS Syntium with °CoolTech™
technology goes to work deep in the heart of the engine. Its strong oil chain performs under extreme
pressure, allowing it to withstand and dissipate aggressively high temperatures and maintain a strong,
stable protective film, even at lower viscosities. Vital components are protected, power output is
maximized, vehicle performance is optimized – and drivers can keep their inner cool.
PETRONAS Syntium is the official technology partner to the 6-times FIA Formula One world
championship-winning MERCEDES AMG PETRONAS Formula One team. We take all of our learnings from
the world’s most demanding test tracks and use them to develop advanced oils for your car, helping to
manage the engine’s temperature, reduce stress on moving parts and prevent heat-related damage.
name: Petronas Syntium 800 SN 10w-40 (API SN/CF) Semi Synthetic 4 ltr
nameWithoutSubText: Petronas Syntium 800 SN 10w-40 (API SN/CF) Semi Synthetic
